---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <main
    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full flex-1 p-2 pt-20 text-center"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-row lg:flex-row items-center justify-center lg:w-1/2">
      <section class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center mx-auto p-2">
        <div
          class="name
        text-2xl
        font-bold
        text-white
        text-start
        w-full"
        >
          Shubham Rasal
        </div>
        <div
          class="intro
          py-2
          text-start lg:text-md text-sm flex items-center justify-center w-full"
        >
          <p>
            I'm a student, developer, and thinker from India. In the digital
            world, I like creating websites and solve problems. Beyond screens,
            I find solace and joy going on long walks. My life blends tech and
            philosophy, coding sessions, and catching thoughts. I love building
            things and helping people. Very active on Twitter.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="location
        text-sm
        text-slate-400
        text-start
        w-full"
        >
          Karnataka, India
        </div>
        <div class="links">
          <div
            class="grid mt-4 grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-8 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-y-4 gap-4 justify-center w-full"
          >
            <a
              href="mailto:bluequbits@gmail.com"
              class="flex items-center justify-center aspect-square shadow-xl shadow-thick hover:bg-primary ring-1 ring-white/10 ring-primary/5 rounded-lg hover:ring-primary/5 hover:ring-white/20 duration-300 group transition-all h-10 w-10"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-mail h-6 w-6 group-hover:scale-125 duration-300 text-primary dark:text-white group-hover text-primary:dark:text-white/50"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke="currentColor"
                fill="none"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
                  d="M3 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-14a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-10z"
                ></path><path d="M3 7l9 6l9 -6"></path></svg
              >
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/Shubham-Rasal"
              target="_blank"
              class="flex items-center justify-center aspect-square shadow-xl shadow-thick hover:bg-primary ring-1 ring-white/10 ring-primary/5 bg-tertiary rounded-lg hover:ring-primary/5 hover:ring-white/20 duration-300 group transition-all h-10 w-10"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-brand-github h-6 w-6 group-hover:scale-125 duration-300 text-primary dark:text-white group-hover text-primary:dark:text-white/50"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke="currentColor"
                fill="none"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
                  d="M9 19c-4.3 1.4 -4.3 -2.5 -6 -3m12 5v-3.5c0 -1 .1 -1.4 -.5 -2c2.8 -.3 5.5 -1.4 5.5 -6a4.6 4.6 0 0 0 -1.3 -3.2a4.2 4.2 0 0 0 -.1 -3.2s-1.1 -.3 -3.5 1.3a12.3 12.3 0 0 0 -6.2 0c-2.4 -1.6 -3.5 -1.3 -3.5 -1.3a4.2 4.2 0 0 0 -.1 3.2a4.6 4.6 0 0 0 -1.3 3.2c0 4.6 2.7 5.7 5.5 6c-.6 .6 -.6 1.2 -.5 2v3.5"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://leetcode.com/_shubham007/"
              target="_blank"
              class="flex items-center justify-center aspect-square shadow-xl shadow-thick hover:bg-primary ring-1 ring-white/10 ring-primary/5 bg-tertiary rounded-lg hover:ring-primary/5 hover:ring-white/20 duration-300 group transition-all h-10 w-10"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-brand-leetcode h-6 w-6 group-hover:scale-125 duration-300 text-primary dark:text-white group-hover text-primary:dark:text-white/50"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke="currentColor"
                fill="none"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
                  d="M12 13h7.5"></path><path d="M9.424 7.268l4.999 -4.999"
                ></path><path
                  d="M16.633 16.644l-2.402 2.415a3.189 3.189 0 0 1 -4.524 0l-3.77 -3.787a3.223 3.223 0 0 1 0 -4.544l3.77 -3.787a3.189 3.189 0 0 1 4.524 0l2.302 2.313"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://twitter.com/bluequbit"
              target="_blank"
              class="flex items-center justify-center aspect-square shadow-xl shadow-thick hover:bg-primary ring-1 ring-white/10 ring-primary/5 bg-tertiary rounded-lg hover:ring-primary/5 hover:ring-white/20 duration-300 group transition-all h-10 w-10"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-brand-x h-6 w-6 group-hover:scale-125 duration-300 text-primary dark:text-white group-hover text-primary:dark:text-white/50"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke="currentColor"
                fill="none"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
                  d="M4 4l11.733 16h4.267l-11.733 -16z"></path><path
                  d="M4 20l6.768 -6.768m2.46 -2.46l6.772 -6.772"></path></svg
              >
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- <section
        class="flex flex-row items-center justify-center p-2 rounded-lg shadow-xl"
      >
        <img
          src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/95695273?s=400&u=f0493387aa4f5e7575010d7d077ed428ddd5892c&v=4"
          alt="Shubham Rasal"
          class="lg:w-20 w-32 rounded-full"
        />
      </section> -->
    </div>
    <section class="flex min-h-0 flex-col gap-y-3 p-2 lg:w-1/2">
      <h2 class="text-xl text-start font-bold">About</h2><div
        class="text-pretty font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground"
      >
        <div
          class="prose max-w-full text-pretty font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground dark:prose-invert"
        >
          <p class="text-start">
            Currently, I'm pursuing my Bachelor's in Information Technology from
            the National Institute of Technology Karnataka, Surathkal. I have
            competed in over a dozen hackathons and have won a few. I have
            interned at couple of companies. I like to write and you can find
            them here. I'm also a big fan of open-source and decentralisation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="flex min-h-0 flex-col gap-y-3 p-2 lg:w-1/2 py-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl text-start font-bold">Work Experience</h2>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-card text-card-foreground">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-2 text-base">
            <h3
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-semibold leading-none"
            >
              <a
                class="hover:underline"
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/oracle/">Oracle</a
              ><span class="inline-flex gap-x-1"></span>
            </h3><time class="text-sm tabular-nums text-gray-500"
              >May 2024 - July 2024</time
            >
          </div><div
            class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-2 text-base"
          >
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm leading-none">
              Server Tech Intern
            </h4><div class="text-sm tabular-nums text-gray-500">
              Bangalore, India
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><div
          class="prose mt-2 max-w-full text-pretty font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground dark:prose-invert"
        >
          <p class="text-start">
            Worked with the Database Cloud Services Team to build a workflow
            visualisation engine (FlowGenie) for internal use of the SRE team.
            Transitioned the existing user interface to a React-based framework
            centered around FlowGenie, enhancing overall usability.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-card text-card-foreground">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-2 text-base">
            <h3
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-semibold leading-none"
            >
              <a
                class="hover:underline"
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/shortsqueeze/"
                >Shortsqueeze</a
              ><span class="inline-flex gap-x-1"></span>
            </h3><time class="text-sm tabular-nums text-gray-500"
              >Nov 2022 - Dec 2022</time
            >
          </div><div
            class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-2 text-base"
          >
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm leading-none">
              Back End Developer
            </h4><div class="text-sm tabular-nums text-gray-500">Remote</div>
          </div>
        </div><div
          class="prose mt-2 max-w-full text-pretty font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground dark:prose-invert"
        >
          <p class="text-start">
            Worked as a Go backend developer and built various APIs including a
            polling service, OTP session-based authentication system, etc.
            Improved performance by leveraging go concurrency for handling
            multiple user logins. Implemented a robust document parsing library
            which handles almost all file formats.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
